title: Episode 171: The Ms. Pat Show Season 2 Debuts Thursday!
description:
Thursday, August 11, is the big day! Season two of the Ms. Pat Show debuts. Ms. Pat takes a minute to pause and reflect on her success these past five years, especially after an appearance on The Daily Show.
